        question="Do you use eco-friendly products for all types of cleaning services?"
        answer="Yes, we are committed to using eco-friendly products for all our cleaning services. Whether it's carpet cleaning, power washing, or window cleaning, we ensure that our products are safe for the environment, your family, and your pets, aligning with our mission to provide sustainable and effective cleaning solutions."
      />
      <FAQ
        question="How often should I schedule cleaning services with Eco Clean?"
        answer="The frequency of cleaning depends on various factors, including the type of space, its usage, and personal preferences. For residential spaces, we recommend professional cleaning every 6 to 12 months, while commercial spaces might need more frequent services. We can work with you to create a customized cleaning schedule that meets your specific needs and ensures your space remains pristine."
      />
    </div>
